WEBVTT

01:43.150 --> 01:46.030
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.170 --> 01:48.990
[Episode 26]

01:53.450 --> 01:54.039
Mrs. Lu,

01:54.420 --> 01:55.330
how'd your check-up go?

01:59.030 --> 01:59.759
Not bad.

02:00.910 --> 02:01.870
I booked a restaurant.

02:01.890 --> 02:02.990
Let's go have dinner.

02:04.210 --> 02:04.930
Don't bother.

02:05.390 --> 02:06.390
I just ate

02:06.410 --> 02:07.630
in the hospital.

02:09.449 --> 02:09.960
Okay.

02:10.020 --> 02:10.680
Well, then,

02:11.180 --> 02:12.210
let's go back first.

02:21.430 --> 02:22.070
Jiang.

02:23.320 --> 02:24.470
Do you police

02:24.500 --> 02:25.950
get any vacation time?

02:26.870 --> 02:27.910
If there are no special missions,

02:27.930 --> 02:29.030
we usually get regular time off.

02:30.270 --> 02:31.870
If your wife

02:31.910 --> 02:33.640
is pregnant and in labor,

02:33.950 --> 02:35.250
do you have paternity leave?

02:35.680 --> 02:36.870
We get

02:36.870 --> 02:37.570
all the usual time off

02:37.750 --> 02:40.390
so long as we're not on a mission.

02:41.870 --> 02:43.190
Then is it dangerous

02:43.470 --> 02:44.590
during the mission?

02:46.310 --> 02:47.420
It's much better now.

02:47.550 --> 02:48.350
But it may be

02:48.350 --> 02:49.230
a little bit dangerous.

02:52.110 --> 02:53.590
Since it's dangerous,

02:55.030 --> 02:56.510
have you considered

02:57.230 --> 02:57.829
changing your job,

02:58.190 --> 02:59.020
like, switching careers?

03:00.470 --> 03:01.240
Mom,

03:01.990 --> 03:03.840
what are you talking about?

03:04.190 --> 03:06.360
Why would he change his job?

03:07.030 --> 03:08.550
Isn't it good to be a policeman?

03:09.350 --> 03:10.630
He's responsible

03:11.070 --> 03:11.990
and reliable.

03:12.310 --> 03:13.280
I like police.

03:16.110 --> 03:17.400
Mrs. Lu,

03:18.120 --> 03:18.990
do you have a problem

03:18.990 --> 03:19.910
with us criminal police?

03:21.710 --> 03:22.290
Mom,

03:22.670 --> 03:23.590
didn't you always want to

03:23.590 --> 03:24.920
go to Songshan?

03:25.390 --> 03:26.520
I'll take leave tomorrow.

03:26.670 --> 03:27.829
Let's go have fun there, okay?

03:28.840 --> 03:29.590
Jiang Chengyi.

03:30.110 --> 03:30.990
Are you free tomorrow?

03:30.990 --> 03:31.700
Let's go together?

03:31.870 --> 03:32.360
OK.

03:32.400 --> 03:32.880
I'll

03:32.910 --> 03:34.960
book the accommodation and restaurants over there.

03:35.190 --> 03:36.130
Is it good?

03:37.310 --> 03:38.040
Don't bother.

03:38.590 --> 03:39.860
I'll head back home tomorrow.

04:13.060 --> 04:16.000
She might be in a bad mood after the check-up.

04:16.029 --> 04:17.310
You can go back and rest.

04:18.390 --> 04:18.950
Okay.

04:19.190 --> 04:20.350
Take this.

04:57.780 --> 04:58.500
Yan.

05:00.350 --> 05:00.900
Yan?

05:01.630 --> 05:02.670
Mom, you're still up?

05:08.180 --> 05:09.310
Tell me.

05:10.630 --> 05:11.790
Do you really like

05:11.790 --> 05:13.070
Jiang Chengyi that much?

05:18.190 --> 05:18.720
Mom,

05:20.210 --> 05:22.790
do you not like him?

05:24.870 --> 05:26.560
I neither like

05:26.590 --> 05:27.750
nor dislike him, actually.

05:28.230 --> 05:29.390
He's a righteous

05:29.830 --> 05:30.990
and nice guy.

05:31.810 --> 05:33.130
If he were my son,

05:33.270 --> 05:34.480
I'd love him for sure.

05:35.790 --> 05:37.030
That's it.

05:37.500 --> 05:38.400
But Yan...

05:38.680 --> 05:39.110
He...

05:39.470 --> 05:39.950
Mom.

05:43.470 --> 05:44.520
I...

05:46.550 --> 05:47.600
I really,

05:47.630 --> 05:49.230
really like Jiang Chengyi.

05:51.780 --> 05:52.909
And we’ve been apart

05:52.940 --> 05:53.909
for years.

05:54.950 --> 05:56.480
This time, we've thought it through

05:58.909 --> 06:00.430
before deciding to get back together.

06:02.350 --> 06:03.710
I don't want to be separated from him again.

06:04.570 --> 06:05.870
As for realistic issues,

06:05.910 --> 06:07.540
I think we will

06:08.050 --> 06:10.040
sort them out smoothly.

06:10.230 --> 06:11.430
But I wish

06:14.750 --> 06:15.790
I can have your support.

06:19.190 --> 06:19.670
Okay.

06:21.870 --> 06:22.800
I respect your thoughts.

06:23.590 --> 06:25.130
I support you

06:25.230 --> 06:27.270
as long as you feel

06:28.830 --> 06:29.750
it's the right decision.

06:33.659 --> 06:34.220
Okay.

06:34.750 --> 06:35.890
Don't stay up too late.

06:36.070 --> 06:36.550
Sleep early.

06:36.710 --> 06:37.230
Okay.

06:38.710 --> 06:39.710
Good night, mom.

06:56.530 --> 06:59.360
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

06:59.450 --> 07:00.310
Oh, Mom...

07:00.350 --> 07:02.250
I'm going to the operating room.

07:02.470 --> 07:04.300
You insisted on leaving on your own without letting us

07:04.430 --> 07:05.070
give you a ride.

07:05.070 --> 07:06.370
Now you've left your stuff here.

07:08.180 --> 07:08.780
Fine.

07:09.070 --> 07:10.080
I’ll help you handle it.

07:18.580 --> 07:19.390
Morning, Captain Jiang.

07:19.410 --> 07:20.010
Captain Jiang.

07:22.070 --> 07:22.920
What are you eating?

07:22.950 --> 07:23.880
You're so into your food.

07:23.910 --> 07:24.630
No... We're not eating.

07:24.630 --> 07:25.320
No?

07:25.590 --> 07:26.070
My goodness.

07:26.110 --> 07:27.030
Greasy food early in the morning?

07:27.110 --> 07:27.720
Seriously?

07:28.240 --> 07:28.810
For more nutrition.

07:29.600 --> 07:30.670
Want some?

07:30.690 --> 07:31.870
No, just keep it for yourself.

07:36.120 --> 07:36.770
Hello?

07:38.150 --> 07:38.790
Jiang Chengyi,

07:38.830 --> 07:39.909
are you up?

07:40.870 --> 07:41.670
I just arrived at the station.

07:41.930 --> 07:43.000
So early!

07:43.800 --> 07:44.870
It's working time.

07:45.490 --> 07:46.900
There's something I need your help with...

07:47.150 --> 07:49.070
My mom is heading back today.

07:49.070 --> 07:50.790
She left her ID card at my home.

07:50.870 --> 07:52.390
Can you help send it to her?

07:54.280 --> 07:55.300
Now...

07:56.820 --> 07:57.430
Okay.

07:57.670 --> 07:58.390
I'll handle it.

07:58.940 --> 07:59.970
Don't get distracted from your work.

08:01.150 --> 08:01.750
Thank you.

08:03.960 --> 08:05.180
I gotta go for a while.

08:05.790 --> 08:07.040
Don't you wanna grab a bite?

08:07.280 --> 08:08.080
Enjoy it yourselves.

08:09.490 --> 08:10.320
Give it to me, bro.

08:10.360 --> 08:10.670
Wait,

08:10.670 --> 08:11.390
just eat the chicken butt.

08:11.390 --> 08:11.830
I bought it.

08:11.830 --> 08:12.430
Chicken butt...

08:12.430 --> 08:13.070
I bought it.

08:22.870 --> 08:23.550
Mrs. Lu...

08:24.830 --> 08:26.150
Use this temporary ID card

08:26.190 --> 08:26.940
for the boarding pass.

08:26.970 --> 08:27.350
Okay.

08:27.390 --> 08:28.160
Thank you.

08:28.770 --> 08:29.230
Well...

08:29.230 --> 08:30.150
I'll send your ID card to you

08:30.190 --> 08:31.070
by mail.

08:31.290 --> 08:31.950
If I

08:31.950 --> 08:32.799
rush back to get it today,

08:32.870 --> 08:33.960
you won't be able to catch the plane.

08:34.120 --> 08:34.690
Okay.

08:36.980 --> 08:38.530
There's still some time before boarding.

08:38.950 --> 08:40.840
Wanna have a chat?

08:41.510 --> 08:42.070
Sure.

08:42.110 --> 08:43.850
Let's sit over there and talk.

08:43.880 --> 08:44.230
Okay.

08:44.270 --> 08:44.670
Let me help.

08:49.230 --> 08:49.970
Mrs. Lu,

08:50.000 --> 08:51.830
what do you want to tell me?

08:54.760 --> 08:56.480
Yan has always been

08:56.630 --> 08:57.760
an independent girl.

08:58.480 --> 08:59.640
She's never made me

08:59.660 --> 09:00.390
worry about anything

09:00.470 --> 09:02.000
since she was a child,

09:02.590 --> 09:04.410
and never has she ever asked me for anything.

09:04.550 --> 09:05.650
Because she knows

09:05.870 --> 09:07.230
it's not easy for me to raise her alone.

09:08.360 --> 09:09.400
There's no child

09:09.430 --> 09:10.840
who doesn't wanna

09:10.990 --> 09:12.790
be spoiled by their parents, right?

09:13.790 --> 09:14.740
But I

09:14.870 --> 09:16.700
couldn't give her a complete home.

09:17.070 --> 09:17.960
I feel guilty.

09:18.670 --> 09:19.960
And she can tell I'm sad.

09:20.830 --> 09:21.670
So she

09:21.690 --> 09:23.850
tells me good news only, never the bad.

09:24.390 --> 09:25.250
I know

09:25.470 --> 09:26.680
she doesn't want me to worry.

09:27.660 --> 09:28.150
I

09:28.190 --> 09:29.800
just do as she wishes,

09:30.910 --> 09:33.070
traveling around the country.

09:33.360 --> 09:34.700
I just want her to know

09:35.070 --> 09:36.040
that her mom

09:36.070 --> 09:38.870
is leading a delightful and fulfilling life.

09:39.580 --> 09:40.990
So she can rest assured.

09:41.630 --> 09:43.170
This is also a special way

09:43.240 --> 09:45.860
for us to get along as mother and daughter.

09:46.230 --> 09:47.950
No news means good news.

09:48.270 --> 09:50.350
We don't usually meet, yet we're not worried.

09:52.710 --> 09:53.790
I've never

09:54.030 --> 09:55.180
doubted

09:55.310 --> 09:56.710
Yan's taste.

09:57.030 --> 09:58.440
And I believe in her judgment.

09:59.710 --> 10:00.470
Jiang,

10:00.900 --> 10:02.060
we haven’t

10:02.670 --> 10:04.060
known each other for long.

10:04.270 --> 10:04.930
But

10:05.080 --> 10:05.990
everyone who's met you

10:05.990 --> 10:07.190
praises you

10:07.210 --> 10:08.520
in front of me,

10:08.710 --> 10:09.830
saying how good you are.

10:14.830 --> 10:15.600
But

10:17.210 --> 10:19.420
as a policeman,

10:20.750 --> 10:22.620
your work schedule is all over the place.

10:23.940 --> 10:26.480
You're always on call or on a mission.

10:26.690 --> 10:27.920
Do you even have to be

10:27.950 --> 10:29.240
on 24-hour standby sometimes?

10:30.360 --> 10:31.690
Indeed.

10:33.440 --> 10:34.290
I know

10:35.390 --> 10:36.750
you are doing great things

10:37.110 --> 10:38.470
to protect the people

10:38.510 --> 10:39.920
and maintain social security.

10:40.550 --> 10:41.620
But I'm a mother.

10:42.550 --> 10:43.920
As a mother,

10:44.230 --> 10:45.110
I also want to protect

10:45.150 --> 10:46.480
my own daughter.

10:47.030 --> 10:48.170
I can be a bit "selfish"

10:48.390 --> 10:49.420
like this, right?

10:50.230 --> 10:50.990
I understand.

10:54.170 --> 10:55.720
I know how hard it is for a woman

10:55.750 --> 10:56.710
to raise a child alone.

10:59.630 --> 11:01.430
Since I've experienced it,

11:01.670 --> 11:03.110
I don't want

11:03.230 --> 11:04.910
my daughter's marriage

11:05.510 --> 11:07.150
to be all about separation.

11:07.430 --> 11:08.230
Do you get it?

11:11.660 --> 11:12.190
Yes.

11:18.140 --> 11:20.670
I couldn't fall asleep last night.

11:21.310 --> 11:22.640
I kept thinking about it.

11:23.240 --> 11:24.760
After I came back this time,

11:24.900 --> 11:26.750
I found Yan a bit different from before.

11:28.260 --> 11:29.900
I pondered over it all night

11:31.510 --> 11:33.760
and finally realized why.

11:35.510 --> 11:36.950
She smiles a lot now.

11:38.290 --> 11:41.110
[Department of Anesthesiology]

11:57.070 --> 11:57.790
Jiang,

11:59.940 --> 12:01.000
do you know

12:03.770 --> 12:06.240
how much this means to me?

12:07.590 --> 12:08.700
It's been eight years. I...

12:09.750 --> 12:10.270
I've never seen

12:10.310 --> 12:11.710
my daughter this happy

12:11.790 --> 12:12.990
over the past eight years.

12:17.550 --> 12:19.310
In this world,

12:19.630 --> 12:20.190
what matters

12:20.190 --> 12:21.600
the most to me?

12:21.670 --> 12:23.780
It's my daughter's happiness, of course!

12:24.190 --> 12:25.080
Right?

12:26.350 --> 12:27.200
Indeed.

12:29.710 --> 12:31.270
I hope you can promise me

12:33.550 --> 12:35.830
to treat Yan well

12:38.030 --> 12:39.990
and never let her cry even once.

12:42.030 --> 12:42.820
No worries.

12:42.950 --> 12:43.550
I promise you.

12:45.120 --> 12:46.040
Also,

12:46.910 --> 12:48.350
if Yan bullies you,

12:49.030 --> 12:49.990
you can tell me.

12:50.390 --> 12:51.590
I'll teach her a lesson,

12:53.590 --> 12:54.750
but you can't.

12:56.590 --> 12:57.310
Got it?

12:59.110 --> 12:59.740
I know.

13:00.020 --> 13:00.880
Please don't worry.

13:08.160 --> 13:11.140
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

13:11.230 --> 13:14.550
[Woman Only]

13:19.670 --> 13:20.440
Not bad.

13:20.550 --> 13:21.120
Honey,

13:21.230 --> 13:21.680
how's it?

13:21.710 --> 13:22.070
Zhong.

13:22.140 --> 13:22.760
It's good!

13:23.090 --> 13:24.140
You can go pay the bill.

13:24.620 --> 13:25.660
Thank you, Lu Yan.

13:29.030 --> 13:29.550
Take a seat.

13:32.720 --> 13:33.680
Look how much

13:33.830 --> 13:34.990
Zhong cares about you.

13:36.270 --> 13:38.020
Actually, he's been quite busy recently.

13:38.190 --> 13:38.760
The new project

13:38.790 --> 13:39.680
he and Wen Peng invested in

13:39.710 --> 13:40.750
is about to kick off.

13:40.880 --> 13:42.660
I didn't want him to come, but he insisted.

13:42.960 --> 13:44.590
As he should!

13:45.590 --> 13:46.670
You gotta catch up with us, too.

13:47.140 --> 13:47.630
Wait,

13:47.630 --> 13:49.190
you've got back together

13:49.310 --> 13:50.840
and met your parents.

13:50.880 --> 13:52.280
Where are you two at in your relationship now?

13:52.500 --> 13:54.030
We

13:54.670 --> 13:56.070
wanna take our time.

13:56.350 --> 13:56.990
Oh, right.

13:57.470 --> 13:58.950
There are still so many cases to solve.

13:59.870 --> 14:01.570
Any new update about that?

14:02.350 --> 14:03.830
I have something to tell you.

14:20.610 --> 14:21.490
I owe an apology to you

14:24.880 --> 14:26.110
and Deng Man.

14:28.190 --> 14:29.310
But it's too late

14:30.440 --> 14:32.150
to fix anything now.

14:35.380 --> 14:36.770
When we got married,

14:38.000 --> 14:38.840
didn't you always say

14:38.870 --> 14:40.150
you wanted to see more of the world?

14:46.310 --> 14:48.060
How about we go for it now?

14:53.030 --> 14:54.140
Let's go together

14:56.210 --> 14:57.350
and never come back.

15:04.870 --> 15:05.750
Zhou Zhicheng

15:05.770 --> 15:07.270
is such a bastard!

15:07.430 --> 15:08.720
He may look decent,

15:08.750 --> 15:10.300
yet he only does dirty things!

15:10.510 --> 15:11.460
Calm down.

15:11.630 --> 15:12.670
I knew you'd end up like this.

15:12.670 --> 15:13.230
So I was hesitant

15:13.270 --> 15:14.060
to tell you.

15:14.080 --> 15:14.540
Wait,

15:14.540 --> 15:15.200
how could he

15:15.230 --> 15:16.390
do that to Man?

15:16.430 --> 15:17.830
Did Jiang Chengyi arrest him?

15:18.270 --> 15:18.950
In this case,

15:18.990 --> 15:20.670
he's at most morally wrong.

15:20.910 --> 15:22.390
We can't sanction him by law.

15:23.350 --> 15:24.800
This hypocrite!

15:25.150 --> 15:25.870
Honey, honey...

15:25.910 --> 15:26.550
-Hey...
-You’re finally here.

15:26.630 --> 15:27.270
-What’s wrong?
-You…

15:27.310 --> 15:27.910
S-She's hungry.

15:27.950 --> 15:28.670
Calm down...

15:28.750 --> 15:29.190
Hungry?

15:29.230 --> 15:30.070
Let's go have lunch then.

15:30.190 --> 15:30.990
-Let’s go.
-Join us, Lu Yan.

15:30.990 --> 15:31.750
Let's eat...

15:33.110 --> 15:34.440
From "Hiroshima Mon Amour"

15:34.500 --> 15:36.160
to the anonymous letter three years ago,

15:36.340 --> 15:39.880
[Deng Man] [Hiroshima Mon Amour] [Unknown Video] [Backup Weibo Account] [Suicide Note] [Anonymous Letter]

15:36.390 --> 15:37.630
all the conditions

15:37.710 --> 15:39.360
are consistent.

15:40.150 --> 15:40.830
But there's one thing

15:40.910 --> 15:41.710
I don't understand.

15:42.110 --> 15:45.930
[Mind Map of Clues about Deng Man]

15:42.590 --> 15:43.550
What is it?

15:45.110 --> 15:46.590
Based on Ding Jing's personality,

15:47.070 --> 15:48.320
would she really make a big deal

15:48.510 --> 15:49.590
out of an anonymous letter?

15:52.600 --> 15:53.800
I did

15:53.990 --> 15:55.270
ask Zhou Zhicheng about this.

15:55.500 --> 15:57.000
The anonymous letter said

15:57.140 --> 15:59.030
Deng Man didn't commit suicide.

15:59.850 --> 16:00.910
Do you have any evidence

16:00.930 --> 16:01.770
or clues?

16:03.510 --> 16:04.570
I have no evidence.

16:05.190 --> 16:06.910
But it must have something to do with Ding Jing.

16:08.110 --> 16:09.040
When the police restarted

16:09.070 --> 16:10.190
the investigation of Deng Man's case,

16:10.680 --> 16:12.100
Ding Jing came to meet me,

16:13.710 --> 16:14.900
saying she could give me money

16:14.920 --> 16:15.970
and let me get treatment

16:16.590 --> 16:17.390
on the condition that

16:18.540 --> 16:19.870
I couldn't tell anyone

16:19.910 --> 16:21.260
anything about Deng Man.

16:22.310 --> 16:23.450
At the beginning of every year,

16:23.550 --> 16:24.550
she would stash 300,000 yuan

16:24.590 --> 16:26.230
in the safe of a club.

16:28.230 --> 16:28.950
That safe

16:28.970 --> 16:30.050
is under her name.

16:31.160 --> 16:32.250
You can go verify it.

16:32.750 --> 16:33.790
You will surely find out.

16:38.470 --> 16:39.110
We're back.

16:39.180 --> 16:41.200
[Mind Map of Clues about Deng Man]

16:43.770 --> 16:45.020
I'll put it on screen.

16:48.390 --> 16:49.270
We've been to this place

16:49.320 --> 16:50.190
mentioned by Zhou Zhicheng.

16:50.310 --> 16:51.270
There is indeed an anonymous safe

16:51.270 --> 16:52.270
belonging to Ding Jing.

16:52.660 --> 16:53.810
But it's been too long.

16:53.910 --> 16:54.790
The CCTV didn't catch

16:54.830 --> 16:56.230
any footage of Chow Zhishing going in or out.

16:56.390 --> 16:58.000
On the night of December 27th,

16:58.230 --> 16:58.990
after Ding Jing attended

16:58.990 --> 17:00.150
the artwork exchange conference,

17:01.110 --> 17:01.870
she once came here.

17:06.380 --> 17:07.839
On the morning of December 28th,

17:08.240 --> 17:09.250
Li Ruonan

17:09.790 --> 17:10.589
also came here.

17:24.450 --> 17:25.550
So,

17:25.670 --> 17:27.140
there was a deal between Ding Jing

17:27.140 --> 17:28.109
and Li Ruonan?

17:28.230 --> 17:29.030
Very likely.

17:35.670 --> 17:36.230
Qin Yue.

17:36.670 --> 17:37.310
Yes.

17:37.470 --> 17:39.550
Go to the detention center to interrogate Li Ruonan.

17:39.620 --> 17:40.750
Show her the video.

17:41.000 --> 17:41.480
Yes.

17:42.730 --> 17:45.580
[Public Security]

17:45.710 --> 17:49.200
[Club Hall]

17:59.630 --> 18:00.160
Tell me

18:00.190 --> 18:01.110
what you were doing there.

18:05.870 --> 18:07.160
You think we couldn't find it out?

18:09.160 --> 18:10.360
Ding Jing promised

18:10.550 --> 18:11.600
to give you money, right?

18:12.550 --> 18:14.200
Why bother asking me since you've found it out?

18:16.430 --> 18:17.430
I was instructed

18:18.750 --> 18:19.760
by Ding Jing.

18:20.790 --> 18:21.720
After Ding Jing

18:22.190 --> 18:23.270
attended the wedding

18:23.300 --> 18:24.840
of Tang Jie and Da Zhong,

18:25.510 --> 18:27.170
she just decided to target Lu Yan.

18:28.830 --> 18:30.010
She told me

18:30.780 --> 18:31.890
that she failed

18:32.390 --> 18:33.590
eight years ago,

18:35.000 --> 18:36.160
and this time, she must make Lu Yan

18:36.190 --> 18:37.150
pay the price.

18:37.500 --> 18:38.290
Liu Yujie,

18:38.650 --> 18:40.430
when on earth will Wang Qiang take action?

18:42.170 --> 18:43.140
I don’t care!

18:43.310 --> 18:44.240
Can you hurry up?

18:44.270 --> 18:45.550
Can you do your job?

18:46.110 --> 18:47.420
Just tell me directly if you can't do it.

18:47.710 --> 18:48.840
You're always delaying.

18:51.830 --> 18:52.510
Liar.

18:52.530 --> 18:54.140
Wasted so much of my time.

18:58.630 --> 18:59.620
Who are you?

19:01.910 --> 19:03.030
I can help you

19:04.250 --> 19:05.220
with what you wanna do.

19:05.590 --> 19:06.470
Help me?

19:06.910 --> 19:07.920
I don't need help.

19:08.540 --> 19:09.180
Lu Yan.

19:10.480 --> 19:11.690
I don’t know what you are talking about.

19:12.400 --> 19:13.400
Wang Qiang

19:13.910 --> 19:14.790
is known for eating his word

19:14.790 --> 19:16.230
in our field.

19:16.580 --> 19:17.990
You can't count on him.

19:18.030 --> 19:18.870
So?

19:19.430 --> 19:20.430
What can you do?

19:20.930 --> 19:22.450
Everything

19:23.200 --> 19:24.120
that Wang Qiang dares not do.

19:27.390 --> 19:28.270
How much do you want?

19:29.000 --> 19:29.850
400,000.

19:31.120 --> 19:32.780
As you required,

19:33.000 --> 19:34.150
I've killed Wang Qianqian.

19:34.190 --> 19:35.860
I'll send you an address in a few days.

19:36.030 --> 19:37.400
I have a safe there.

19:37.950 --> 19:39.200
Go get the money yourself.

19:39.790 --> 19:40.350
Okay.

19:40.910 --> 19:41.570
Also,

19:41.990 --> 19:42.910
don't call me

19:42.910 --> 19:43.840
ever again.

19:44.430 --> 19:45.810
I'll leave money

19:45.910 --> 19:46.980
in the safe

19:47.270 --> 19:48.790
and messages about what I want you to do next.

20:07.950 --> 20:08.710
So,

20:10.110 --> 20:12.090
Ding Jing asked me to pretend to be Deng Man

20:12.550 --> 20:14.040
and kill Wang Qianqian.

20:14.510 --> 20:15.760
Yet she didn't pay me.

20:16.230 --> 20:18.190
So I asked her to meet me in Jifu Village

20:18.670 --> 20:20.410
and tortured her for days.

20:20.990 --> 20:22.470
She told me she went bankrupt

20:22.470 --> 20:23.330
and ran out of money.

20:23.670 --> 20:25.530
Then you guys came out of nowhere.

20:25.960 --> 20:26.950
I had no choice

20:28.380 --> 20:29.770
but to kill her.

20:31.440 --> 20:32.840
You finally started to tell the truth.

20:39.270 --> 20:40.310
Finally said something, huh?

20:44.670 --> 20:45.610
Tell me

20:45.830 --> 20:47.270
what you were looking for

20:47.750 --> 20:48.710
in Ding Jing's house.

20:50.830 --> 20:51.630
Money.

20:51.710 --> 20:52.680
Money?

20:53.710 --> 20:54.750
In the age of mobile payments,

20:54.870 --> 20:56.030
who would put cash at home?

20:59.850 --> 21:01.780
You took such a big risk

21:01.870 --> 21:03.020
to go search Ding Jing's house

21:03.310 --> 21:04.230
for something

21:04.230 --> 21:06.010
more important than money

21:07.220 --> 21:08.930
to you and the one behind you,

21:09.910 --> 21:10.480
right?

21:17.440 --> 21:19.120
I've told you everything.

21:20.670 --> 21:22.190
What else do you want me to say?

21:25.910 --> 21:27.350
You've kept silent for so long

21:28.230 --> 21:29.110
since you came here.

21:29.680 --> 21:30.870
Yet after watching

21:30.870 --> 21:32.140
a random video today,

21:33.010 --> 21:34.110
you spit it all out

21:35.030 --> 21:36.710
and blamed it all on Ding Jing.

21:37.510 --> 21:38.550
A dead person

21:40.130 --> 21:41.270
can't say anything about it.

21:42.030 --> 21:42.590
Right?

21:45.450 --> 21:46.960
You beat around the bush

21:48.350 --> 21:49.740
and put on such a big show

21:50.190 --> 21:51.590
just to help the person behind you

21:51.670 --> 21:53.430
to get rid of the suspicion.

22:02.070 --> 22:02.790
Fine.

22:02.970 --> 22:03.990
You still helped me

22:03.990 --> 22:04.990
confirm that

22:05.590 --> 22:06.660
you

22:07.030 --> 22:08.190
and Coach Zhou

22:09.750 --> 22:11.260
are manipulated by the same person.

22:14.190 --> 22:15.470
What are you talking about?

22:16.340 --> 22:17.710
I don't understand at all.

22:18.270 --> 22:19.470
It doesn't matter if you don't get it.

22:20.550 --> 22:21.490
I gave you a chance,

22:22.100 --> 22:23.190
yet you let it slip.

22:24.750 --> 22:25.630
Coach Zhou

22:25.630 --> 22:26.700
is not as tight-lipped as you are.

22:31.290 --> 22:36.750
[Public Security of the New era]

22:31.310 --> 22:32.310
You're amazing,

22:32.310 --> 22:32.950
Captain Jiang.

22:33.680 --> 22:35.190
When did you find out

22:35.270 --> 22:36.550
the video was made intentionally?

22:38.390 --> 22:40.470
Because of what Zhou Zhicheng said.

22:41.030 --> 22:42.190
He wanted us to investigate

22:42.230 --> 22:43.550
the safe of the club so eagerly.

22:44.150 --> 22:45.240
So there must be something wrong.

22:46.790 --> 22:48.270
So you already suspected

22:48.290 --> 22:49.660
that Zhou Zhicheng deliberately

22:49.750 --> 22:50.670
revealed this clue to you?

22:52.070 --> 22:53.260
I was also not sure about it.

22:53.640 --> 22:55.230
But I'd like to give it a try.

22:56.470 --> 22:57.030
Okay.

22:58.040 --> 22:59.060
I'll leave you to it.

22:59.190 --> 23:00.330
I have classes in the afternoon.

23:00.710 --> 23:01.150
Bye.

23:01.230 --> 23:01.710
Bye-bye.

23:18.150 --> 23:18.910
Coach Zhou,

23:18.910 --> 23:19.550
are you heading out?

23:19.550 --> 23:19.950
Yeah.

23:19.950 --> 23:21.370
Taking my wife out for a walk.

23:56.320 --> 23:57.360
Let's go. Get off.

24:05.750 --> 24:06.600
Stop.

24:06.790 --> 24:07.350
What's wrong?

24:07.510 --> 24:08.110
It's Zhou Zhicheng.

24:08.130 --> 24:09.250
Call Captain Jiang!

24:13.290 --> 24:13.810
Got it.

24:14.420 --> 24:15.310
Follow him.

24:15.330 --> 24:16.330
I'll be right there.

24:16.670 --> 24:17.310
Okay.

24:22.160 --> 24:25.360
[Anshan, Ninghai Public Security
Criminal Investigation Unit]

25:09.690 --> 25:10.440
[Lei Yiming]

25:11.630 --> 25:12.190
Hello?

25:12.270 --> 25:13.050
Captain Jiang,

25:13.150 --> 25:13.870
I found Zhou Zhishing's car

25:13.910 --> 25:15.010
heading for the airport.

25:15.310 --> 25:16.610
I'll send you the pic of his license plate number.

25:16.720 --> 25:17.270
OK.

25:17.270 --> 25:18.180
Do your best to follow him.

25:18.430 --> 25:19.680
Keep in touch. I'm on my way there.

25:19.830 --> 25:20.430
Got it.

26:18.230 --> 26:18.790
Sorry about that.

26:18.830 --> 26:19.470
Sorry.

26:19.580 --> 26:20.750
How could you drive like that?

27:05.290 --> 27:08.140
[Office of Criminal Investigation Unit]

27:08.260 --> 27:12.990
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

27:08.530 --> 27:09.270
We didn't expect

27:09.310 --> 27:09.910
Zhou Zhicheng

27:09.960 --> 27:10.990
would run the red light.

27:11.350 --> 27:12.270
And that truck driver

27:12.270 --> 27:13.070
drove so fast.

27:13.070 --> 27:14.430
Cheng couldn't even dodge it.

27:14.590 --> 27:15.750
Luckily, Captain Jiang arrived in time

27:15.820 --> 27:16.750
and caught him.

27:16.870 --> 27:17.790
As long as you're safe.

27:18.790 --> 27:19.870
Based on what I just found,

27:20.390 --> 27:21.510
this truck driver

27:21.550 --> 27:22.390
is a habitual offender

27:23.320 --> 27:24.900
with countless violation records.

27:25.030 --> 27:25.750
He claimed that he was drunk

27:25.750 --> 27:26.510
and didn't see us.

27:28.630 --> 27:29.650
What about Zhou Zhicheng?

27:29.750 --> 27:30.470
Still the same old thing claim.

27:30.730 --> 27:32.370
He said he was sending his wife, Lin Chunmei,

27:32.870 --> 27:34.090
to the hospital as she was under the weather.

27:34.230 --> 27:34.870
He ran the red light

27:35.030 --> 27:35.990
in a hurry.

27:36.590 --> 27:37.830
He said you also asked him yesterday,

27:37.870 --> 27:39.060
when he said the same reason

27:39.230 --> 27:40.030
and told the truth.

27:42.910 --> 27:44.020
Should I interrogate him again?

27:45.790 --> 27:46.550
Not now.

27:47.710 --> 27:48.830
If he's really

27:48.870 --> 27:49.880
been controlled by someone,

27:50.590 --> 27:52.550
he's already complicit in the crime.

27:53.410 --> 27:54.210
He won't tell the truth.

27:55.350 --> 27:55.950
It's okay.

27:56.630 --> 27:57.440
Don't be discouraged.

27:57.990 --> 27:59.270
It's easy to deal with Zhou Zhicheng.

27:59.510 --> 28:00.550
Check his phone first.

28:00.780 --> 28:02.550
See who he's contacted.

28:03.230 --> 28:04.820
Let's interrogate him after we find the clues.

28:05.110 --> 28:06.180
He can't hold on for long.

28:06.480 --> 28:07.830
And don't forget

28:07.960 --> 28:09.050
about the truck driver.

28:09.980 --> 28:11.260
Since he's a habitual offender,

28:11.590 --> 28:13.270
let's investigate him with his records

28:13.630 --> 28:15.550
and see who's recruited him.

28:15.630 --> 28:16.190
Got it.

28:15.670 --> 28:23.600
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

28:16.310 --> 28:17.110
Let's get to work.

28:19.750 --> 28:20.870
Remember to be careful

28:20.910 --> 28:21.830
on your following missions.

28:22.950 --> 28:23.470
Got it.

28:25.970 --> 28:29.170
[Who's this old hag? She's nowhere near good enough for our idol.]

28:32.980 --> 28:35.430
[Is she insane? How shameless!]

28:32.980 --> 28:35.430
[Who is this teacher? She doesn't deserve our Feng! Doesn't she know how old she is?]

28:55.950 --> 28:56.570
Hello,

28:56.630 --> 28:58.700
the number you've dialed is unavailable.

28:58.790 --> 28:59.640
Sorry...

29:04.650 --> 29:06.010
Hao, I gotta go.

29:06.710 --> 29:07.240
Bofeng,

29:08.310 --> 29:09.400
Mr. Wen specifically asked me

29:09.430 --> 29:10.730
to keep an eye on you.

29:11.400 --> 29:12.770
Please don't make it hard for me.

29:25.030 --> 29:25.510
Bofeng,

29:26.110 --> 29:26.790
didn’t Mr. Wen

29:26.810 --> 29:27.790
already send the PR staff

29:27.830 --> 29:29.470
to sign the agreement with Professor Yu?

29:29.500 --> 29:30.890
They won't push her for sure.

29:32.030 --> 29:33.140
What agreement?

29:33.170 --> 29:34.150
Just ask her to help

29:34.150 --> 29:35.430
record a clarification video.

29:37.190 --> 29:38.210
A clarification video?

29:38.830 --> 29:39.510
Didn't Mr. Wen say

29:39.510 --> 29:40.470
they'd pay the PR company

29:40.510 --> 29:42.230
to remove the photos directly?

29:42.550 --> 29:43.210
Yes!

29:43.350 --> 29:44.270
But like always,

29:44.310 --> 29:45.060
we must make her

29:45.060 --> 29:46.010
sign an agreement.

29:46.150 --> 29:46.990
Aren't we always

29:46.990 --> 29:48.110
handling it in this way?

29:48.390 --> 29:49.820
I'm speechless.

29:51.710 --> 29:53.000
She's different from others.

29:53.470 --> 29:53.990
Bofeng...

29:55.460 --> 29:56.110
Just let me out.

29:56.190 --> 29:56.670
I promise

29:56.670 --> 29:57.830
I'll be back before twelve.

29:58.310 --> 29:59.190
I won't cause any trouble.

29:59.980 --> 30:01.220
Don't tell Mr. Wen.

30:08.750 --> 30:10.070
I knew you'd be here.

30:10.470 --> 30:12.430
Why are you here again?

30:13.470 --> 30:14.110
Well,

30:16.110 --> 30:16.830
I came

30:16.910 --> 30:18.520
to see if you're okay.

30:19.070 --> 30:20.070
I just want to

30:21.030 --> 30:22.110
apologize to you in person.

30:23.230 --> 30:23.950
I'm sorry.

30:28.660 --> 30:29.270
Professor Yu,

30:29.270 --> 30:30.790
I heard that a PR team

30:30.820 --> 30:31.830
contacted you, right?

30:32.030 --> 30:33.230
They even asked you to record

30:33.790 --> 30:34.820
a clarification video.

30:36.090 --> 30:37.590
But I refused.

30:38.630 --> 30:39.110
I'm sorry.

30:39.140 --> 30:40.150
I caused you so much trouble.

30:40.600 --> 30:41.460
Alright...

30:41.960 --> 30:42.950
No more bows.

30:43.670 --> 30:45.130
Your boss has apologized to me.

30:45.550 --> 30:46.310
Have you

30:46.310 --> 30:47.390
been on Weibo these days?

30:48.150 --> 30:48.790
Yep.

30:49.510 --> 30:51.830
I've checked all the major social media.

30:52.700 --> 30:53.750
These fans

30:53.790 --> 30:54.950
are quite interesting.

30:55.430 --> 30:57.130
They're so creative in cursing.

30:57.630 --> 30:59.670
It's way beyond my imagination.

31:00.370 --> 31:01.110
I really shouldn't have

31:01.110 --> 31:02.350
taken you there.

31:03.270 --> 31:04.340
It's all my fault.

31:04.510 --> 31:05.400
No, I-I'm sorry...

31:05.430 --> 31:06.350
Stop bowing.

31:06.470 --> 31:07.750
You've bowed three times.

31:08.430 --> 31:10.030
It's almost like at my funeral.

31:13.150 --> 31:13.810
Are you

31:14.070 --> 31:14.900
not angry?

31:15.230 --> 31:16.130
I'm not.

31:16.390 --> 31:17.110
Don't you mind

31:17.150 --> 31:18.050
their cursing at you?

31:18.190 --> 31:19.820
I'm not a kid.

31:20.310 --> 31:21.350
Everyone can say something

31:21.470 --> 31:22.990
on the Internet.

31:23.740 --> 31:25.070
This drama will end in a few days.

31:26.750 --> 31:27.550
Then, Professor Yu,

31:27.710 --> 31:29.190
can you add me again

31:29.270 --> 31:29.990
on WeChat?

31:30.690 --> 31:31.680
No.

31:32.100 --> 31:33.750
I never add back any contact I delete.

31:35.790 --> 31:36.230
OK.

31:36.230 --> 31:37.820
Forget about WeChat for now.

31:38.070 --> 31:39.200
Do you have anything to eat?

31:42.050 --> 31:44.090
I've been worried about you these days.

31:44.910 --> 31:45.670
Not until I saw you

31:45.670 --> 31:46.900
did I remember I didn't eat anything.

31:46.940 --> 31:47.950
I suddenly got hungry.

32:02.760 --> 32:03.900
I've got this only.

32:03.990 --> 32:04.830
Finish it and leave.

32:17.180 --> 32:17.850
Gosh.

32:18.030 --> 32:19.070
Since Mr. Wen

32:19.110 --> 32:20.250
brought me to the show business,

32:20.430 --> 32:21.630
I've never had any instant noodles.

32:21.910 --> 32:22.880
This is the first bowl.

32:28.610 --> 32:30.440
Are you close to Mr. Wen?

32:30.820 --> 32:32.090
We're on really, really good terms.

32:32.700 --> 32:33.830
Were it not for Mr. Wen,

32:33.870 --> 32:34.870
I wouldn't be where I am today.

32:37.310 --> 32:38.570
How did you know each other?

32:39.110 --> 32:40.760
At that time,

32:40.830 --> 32:41.470
I was handing out

32:41.470 --> 32:42.730
leaflets at the mall entrance.

32:42.830 --> 32:44.120
Then he came to me and asked

32:44.190 --> 32:45.630
if I wanted to change my job.

32:46.550 --> 32:47.070
That's it.

32:48.310 --> 32:49.230
So he really

32:49.230 --> 32:50.350
signed you on the street?

32:50.750 --> 32:51.230
Yep.

32:52.820 --> 32:53.790
He's got a good taste.

32:55.790 --> 32:56.200
Professor Yu,

32:56.230 --> 32:57.690
are you praising me for being handsome?

32:59.670 --> 33:01.100
Have you finished?

33:05.830 --> 33:06.630
Actually, Mr. Wen

33:06.670 --> 33:07.590
is really nice to me.

33:08.830 --> 33:09.670
See? I got

33:09.750 --> 33:11.290
into such a big trouble.

33:12.150 --> 33:13.350
The company suffered a huge financial loss.

33:13.370 --> 33:14.840
Yet he didn't scold me even once.

33:15.190 --> 33:16.520
Then why did you still come to me?

33:16.790 --> 33:17.440
I was worried

33:17.470 --> 33:18.610
something might happen to you.

33:19.400 --> 33:20.970
I could feel relieved at the sight of you.

33:29.270 --> 33:30.050
By the way,

33:30.560 --> 33:32.130
did anyone know

33:32.570 --> 33:33.580
you came to meet me that day?

33:34.510 --> 33:35.310
No.

33:35.510 --> 33:36.820
I didn't tell anyone when I came out.

33:36.840 --> 33:38.260
Only my assistant knew it.

33:40.330 --> 33:41.820
I've been curious.

33:42.950 --> 33:44.230
You came to me that day,

33:44.350 --> 33:45.560
and we went out for dinner

33:45.590 --> 33:47.230
all on a whim.

33:48.290 --> 33:49.230
How could we get caught

33:49.230 --> 33:50.550
on camera as soon as we sat down?

33:51.570 --> 33:52.470
Could it be that

33:52.510 --> 33:53.540
the man had been following us

33:53.540 --> 33:54.630
from the school?

33:55.630 --> 33:56.530
No.

33:57.400 --> 33:58.320
As police officers,

33:58.350 --> 33:59.470
we have professional habits.

33:59.890 --> 34:00.720
Whenever we go out,

34:00.750 --> 34:01.470
we'll check if anyone's

34:01.510 --> 34:02.350
following us.

34:03.070 --> 34:04.630
I also checked that day.

34:04.660 --> 34:05.230
No followers.

34:07.800 --> 34:08.790
That's weird.

34:08.830 --> 34:09.750
Who could it be?

34:11.510 --> 34:12.550
Give me your phone.

34:16.270 --> 34:16.949
Unlock it.

34:34.710 --> 34:35.820
Who is this guy?

34:38.170 --> 34:41.420
[Location Information] [Ninghai Police Academy]

34:38.739 --> 34:39.949
0713.

34:41.760 --> 34:43.270
Isn't it Hao's birthday?

34:44.230 --> 34:46.020
It's my assistant's birthday.

34:46.070 --> 34:48.790
[Ninghai Police Academy]

34:46.270 --> 34:47.230
Your phone location

34:47.230 --> 34:49.550
has been tracked by this 0713 all the time.

34:51.310 --> 34:52.110
Hao?

35:20.760 --> 35:23.120
[Remember to eat!]

36:29.430 --> 36:30.550
Why did you do that?

36:33.470 --> 36:34.460
I'm sorry, Mr. Wen.

36:36.320 --> 36:37.500
How much did they pay you

36:37.550 --> 36:38.470
to buy these photos?

36:40.190 --> 36:41.120
50,000 yuan.

36:44.590 --> 36:45.310
50,000?

36:47.070 --> 36:48.180
Are you short of money?

36:49.000 --> 36:49.670
I told you

36:49.670 --> 36:50.360
if you were

36:50.390 --> 36:51.110
cash-strapped,

36:51.110 --> 36:51.910
you must tell me

36:51.990 --> 36:52.750
and turn to me.

36:55.230 --> 36:56.590
Sorry, Mr. Wen. I'm so sorry.

36:58.990 --> 36:59.470
Alright.

36:59.500 --> 37:00.530
Go meet HR for the final paycheck.

37:13.940 --> 37:15.650
Mr. Wen, you're such a nice guy.

37:17.190 --> 37:18.710
He caused such a big trouble.

37:18.840 --> 37:20.490
You finally found the reason,

37:20.750 --> 37:22.160
yet you just fired him

37:22.230 --> 37:23.190
without claiming compensation.

37:25.070 --> 37:26.190
A little assistant

37:26.270 --> 37:28.320
earns only a few thousand yuan a month.

37:28.340 --> 37:29.900
How much can he compensate?

37:33.430 --> 37:34.120
Mr. Wen,

37:34.150 --> 37:35.150
are you always this chill?

37:35.700 --> 37:37.220
No wonder you can succeed in your career.

37:39.070 --> 37:39.590
What?

37:39.960 --> 37:41.970
You wanna see me scolding my subordinate?

37:42.600 --> 37:43.630
Not really.

37:44.530 --> 37:45.950
But some people are calm

37:45.990 --> 37:47.010
for real.

37:47.430 --> 37:48.310
And some

37:48.830 --> 37:50.270
are trying their best

37:50.290 --> 37:51.650
to suppress their emotions.

37:52.330 --> 37:53.560
Just like the children

37:53.590 --> 37:54.990
we analyzed in the past cases.

37:55.710 --> 37:56.910
They might have suffered

37:56.990 --> 37:58.390
a lot of traumas in childhood.

37:59.270 --> 38:00.510
So when they grow up,

38:00.590 --> 38:01.710
they're seldom open

38:01.750 --> 38:02.630
about their feelings.

38:03.720 --> 38:04.470
Of course,

38:04.490 --> 38:05.690
I’m not referring to you, Mr. Wen.

38:09.820 --> 38:10.600
Professor Yu,

38:11.400 --> 38:12.920
is your occupational habit kicking in?

38:16.660 --> 38:17.910
Anyway,

38:18.060 --> 38:19.820
it's my fault.

38:19.990 --> 38:21.190
I didn't manage my subordinates well,

38:21.310 --> 38:22.680
who caused you trouble.

38:22.830 --> 38:24.030
I'm really sorry.

38:24.480 --> 38:25.740
You don't have to apologize.

38:26.510 --> 38:27.510
Yu Bofeng

38:27.510 --> 38:29.140
seems quite concerned about his assistant.

38:29.390 --> 38:30.830
You should spend some time

38:30.910 --> 38:32.190
comforting him.

38:32.430 --> 38:33.270
Didn't you

38:33.430 --> 38:34.630
already comfort him?

38:34.910 --> 38:36.130
We were just chatting.

38:36.470 --> 38:37.230
I believe you.

38:38.270 --> 38:39.700
But now,

38:39.730 --> 38:41.080
at this critical time,

38:41.590 --> 38:42.870
I hope you can

38:43.010 --> 38:44.460
keep a distance from him

38:44.870 --> 38:45.710
Don't go see him

38:45.750 --> 38:47.330
or let him come to see you.

38:47.940 --> 38:49.470
We're adults.

38:49.790 --> 38:51.320
No one wants to cause anyone trouble.

38:52.420 --> 38:53.490
No worries, Mr. Wen.

39:29.200 --> 39:29.670
Peng,

39:32.740 --> 39:34.880
I-I'm feeling really down.

39:37.190 --> 39:37.870
I know.

39:38.400 --> 39:40.540
So I came to drink with you.

39:46.400 --> 39:47.260
Because of Hao.

39:52.240 --> 39:53.380
I fired him.

39:54.710 --> 39:55.430
I must

39:55.470 --> 39:56.900
do this for the company.

39:57.310 --> 39:58.360
But don't worry.

39:58.510 --> 40:00.020
I gave him some money

40:00.150 --> 40:00.750
which could

40:00.750 --> 40:01.980
last him a while.

40:02.270 --> 40:03.390
After all, he's been with you for three years.

40:05.470 --> 40:06.100
Thank you, Peng.

40:07.430 --> 40:08.520
You know

40:08.550 --> 40:09.870
I don't have many friends.

40:11.850 --> 40:12.600
So I think...

40:12.670 --> 40:13.320
So,

40:13.390 --> 40:14.590
you value your friends

40:15.750 --> 40:16.910
and are afraid of being hurt by them.

40:23.530 --> 40:24.190
Bofeng,

40:25.310 --> 40:26.880
as I told you before,

40:27.340 --> 40:28.500
you can only

40:29.030 --> 40:30.350
trust yourself in this world,

40:31.710 --> 40:33.460
Your family may abandon you.

40:33.560 --> 40:35.410
Your friends may set you up.

40:35.710 --> 40:36.470
One day,

40:36.510 --> 40:37.780
even your beloved one

40:37.990 --> 40:38.910
may betray you.

40:39.500 --> 40:40.630
But I don't think so.

40:43.710 --> 40:44.750
I think the person I love

40:44.790 --> 40:46.310
will never betray me.

40:52.660 --> 40:53.790
Of course, you won't betray me either,

40:53.810 --> 40:54.330
Peng.

40:56.140 --> 40:56.870
I've seen you

40:56.920 --> 40:58.510
as my closest friend from the very beginning.

41:01.680 --> 41:02.250
Bofeng,

41:02.910 --> 41:03.470
I'm sorry.

41:04.750 --> 41:05.390
As your brother,

41:05.390 --> 41:06.270
I didn't protect you well.

41:07.490 --> 41:09.150
You don't have to apologize to me.

41:09.270 --> 41:10.580
I'm the only one to blame

41:10.670 --> 41:11.790
for the whole mess.

41:11.870 --> 41:13.320
It has nothing to do with you.

41:28.120 --> 41:29.160
I remember a saying.

41:31.330 --> 41:33.270
God sees everything.

41:33.830 --> 41:35.260
Does God really know

41:35.800 --> 41:37.190
what people are thinking

41:37.550 --> 41:38.390
and what they are doing?

41:40.350 --> 41:41.150
Maybe

41:41.990 --> 41:43.360
even God can't see through it sometimes.

41:44.750 --> 41:45.070
Peng,

41:45.070 --> 41:46.190
this question's way too deep.

41:46.230 --> 41:47.550
I've never thought about it before.

42:01.270 --> 42:01.910
Morning.

42:06.230 --> 42:07.640
How did I get back yesterday, Peng?

42:08.980 --> 42:10.180
How?

42:10.470 --> 42:12.450
I carried you back, of course.

42:14.030 --> 42:15.120
What are you cooking?

42:15.870 --> 42:17.040
Smells so good.

42:19.990 --> 42:21.040
Some soup

42:21.060 --> 42:22.190
to sober you up.

42:24.010 --> 42:25.380
My boss is so nice to me.

42:25.830 --> 42:26.870
He carried me back at night

42:26.890 --> 42:28.140
and made me food in the morning.

42:40.390 --> 42:41.150
Hello, what’s up?

42:41.760 --> 42:43.020
Mr. Wen, we're in trouble.

42:43.340 --> 42:44.110
Check your Weibo.

42:54.450 --> 42:55.850
Ask the PR company to work immediately

42:55.990 --> 42:57.120
and keep things under control in the media.

42:59.210 --> 43:03.830
[Can't believe the police forced a person to death! How dare they?]

42:59.210 --> 43:03.830
[The exposure of Yu Bofeng's real identity! His adoptive mother was wrongly accused as a thief.]

43:04.170 --> 43:04.960
No way.

43:06.380 --> 43:07.030
What?

43:07.030 --> 43:08.110
They say my Aunt Wang was a thief?

43:08.860 --> 43:09.870
Aunt Wang could never

43:09.870 --> 43:10.380
be a thief.

43:11.280 --> 43:13.140
There's no way she could've been one!

43:13.230 --> 43:14.590
Calm down.

43:14.610 --> 43:15.680
How can I calm down?

43:15.710 --> 43:16.830
See what they're saying!

43:17.110 --> 43:17.830
Calm down a bit

43:17.910 --> 43:19.200
and recall

43:19.400 --> 43:20.070
how your family

43:20.070 --> 43:21.190
told you about Aunt Wang's death.

43:21.380 --> 43:22.190
My hometown fellows said

43:22.190 --> 43:23.270
Aunt Wang had a heart attack

43:23.360 --> 43:24.070
and suddenly passed away.

43:24.380 --> 43:25.190
When I went back,

43:25.230 --> 43:26.180
she was already gone.

43:26.390 --> 43:27.240
Why don't you make a call

43:27.270 --> 43:28.030
to confirm it?

43:28.190 --> 43:29.470
Aunt Wang has no other relatives.

43:29.470 --> 43:30.550
Who can I ask?

43:38.590 --> 43:39.550
Where are you going?

43:40.510 --> 43:41.940
I'm going to ask Jiang Chengyi.

43:42.120 --> 43:43.420
You can't go.

43:44.110 --> 43:45.030
Why can't I?

43:45.670 --> 43:46.910
Don't you know how much

43:46.910 --> 43:48.030
Aunt Wang matters to me?

43:48.230 --> 43:50.480
Were it not for her, I would have died long ago!

43:50.710 --> 43:51.510
Aunt Wang could never

43:51.510 --> 43:52.570
be a thief.

43:53.070 --> 43:53.950
The police must

43:53.950 --> 43:54.750
have framed her!

43:54.830 --> 43:56.270
I understand how you feel.

43:56.270 --> 43:56.790
But now,

43:56.830 --> 43:58.050
you can't go anywhere.

43:58.930 --> 43:59.790
Do you know how many people

43:59.830 --> 44:00.710
are watching you out there?

44:01.980 --> 44:03.290
Give me some time

44:03.430 --> 44:04.430
to deal with this,

44:04.470 --> 44:04.960
OK?

44:05.120 --> 44:05.750
Then what should I do?

44:05.750 --> 44:07.170
Sit and wait at home?

44:07.230 --> 44:09.190
Let them talk nonsense online?

44:10.040 --> 44:10.550
Bofeng.

44:12.070 --> 44:12.590
Quiet.

44:12.830 --> 44:13.490
Calm down.

44:14.070 --> 44:14.790
Stay sober.

44:15.310 --> 44:16.090
Take a deep breath.

44:16.390 --> 44:17.030
Take a deep breath.

44:17.910 --> 44:18.590
Take a deep breath.

44:22.000 --> 44:23.010
Listen to me now.

44:23.380 --> 44:24.620
Don't go anywhere.

44:25.100 --> 44:26.440
Just stay at home

44:26.830 --> 44:27.990
and don't contact anyone.

44:28.830 --> 44:29.630
Understand?

44:49.520 --> 44:53.520
[2006]

44:53.310 --> 44:54.960
What a serious car accident!

44:56.270 --> 44:57.700
I heard a couple died in it.

44:57.700 --> 44:58.550
Poor things.

44:59.110 --> 45:00.860
Is that kid their son?

45:01.130 --> 45:03.200
Yeah, poor little thing.

45:03.390 --> 45:05.440
He lost his parents at such a young age.

45:05.740 --> 45:07.490
How is he supposed to live?

45:07.920 --> 45:10.370
Poor kid.

45:14.750 --> 45:16.250
The Yu family is really a tragedy.

45:16.680 --> 45:17.630
There's only a child left.

45:17.660 --> 45:18.870
How can he survive in this world?

45:24.360 --> 45:25.290
Where are you going?

45:30.930 --> 45:32.480
Mom!

45:35.550 --> 45:36.910
-Mom...
-It’s okay.

45:37.070 --> 45:38.190
It's okay. Don't be afraid.

45:39.110 --> 45:39.990
It's okay.

45:40.070 --> 45:42.110
I got you. Don't cry...

45:43.540 --> 45:46.560
[Yilin Barbershop]

45:55.830 --> 45:56.650
I've paid.

45:56.790 --> 45:57.230
Okay.

46:01.780 --> 46:03.180
Your heart is aching again?

46:07.510 --> 46:08.110
It's okay.

46:09.170 --> 46:10.420
I'll be fine after taking the medicine.

46:10.710 --> 46:11.880
Well,

46:12.390 --> 46:13.710
given your poor health, why do you

46:13.760 --> 46:15.060
insist on taking care of a child?

46:15.110 --> 46:15.800
It's not that

46:15.830 --> 46:17.240
I don't allow you to adopt him.

46:17.350 --> 46:18.620
He is quite pitiful.

46:18.740 --> 46:20.030
But have you ever thought

46:20.170 --> 46:21.170
about your own future?

46:22.510 --> 46:24.130
I'm doing great now.

46:24.350 --> 46:25.630
Not at all!

46:25.750 --> 46:27.590
You've got the old, the little, and the ill in your family.

46:27.710 --> 46:28.380
You

46:28.460 --> 46:29.620
are just too kind.

46:32.220 --> 46:32.670
Here.

46:32.950 --> 46:33.670
Take this.

46:35.750 --> 46:36.190
Well...

46:36.250 --> 46:37.820
Don't feed the boy bread only.

46:37.940 --> 46:39.150
Go buy him some food.

46:54.860 --> 46:57.980
[The murderers who forced Yu Bofeng's foster mother to death, come out and say something!]

46:58.000 --> 47:00.000
[How can such a person be a teacher? She should be fired! @Ninghai Police Academy]

47:00.030 --> 47:03.520
[Fire the murderer. @Ninghai Police Academy]

47:33.420 --> 47:34.820
Hello, Bofeng.

47:34.990 --> 47:35.630
Aunt Wang,

47:35.650 --> 47:37.190
I'll be discharged tomorrow.

47:38.160 --> 47:39.630
Discharged tomorrow?

47:39.920 --> 47:40.710
Yes.

47:40.910 --> 47:41.470
Then,

47:42.150 --> 47:43.630
make sure the doctor gives you

47:43.710 --> 47:45.480
a thorough check-up before you leave.

47:45.630 --> 47:46.070
Got it.

47:46.070 --> 47:46.580
Don't worry.

47:46.580 --> 47:47.390
I told the doctor

47:47.390 --> 47:48.230
I'd hold off

47:48.270 --> 47:49.070
on the last hospital bill.

47:50.190 --> 47:51.620
I have money.

47:53.080 --> 47:53.880
Tomorrow.

47:54.510 --> 47:56.810
I'll go to the hospital to pay the bill tomorrow.

47:57.350 --> 47:58.220
Don't worry about it.

47:59.300 --> 48:00.450
Thank you, Aunt Wang.

48:00.490 --> 48:01.430
I'm hanging up.

48:06.210 --> 48:08.490
Haven't got enough money for Bofeng's hospital fee.

48:08.910 --> 48:10.500
What should I do?

48:13.700 --> 48:14.530
Sir,

48:14.910 --> 48:16.590
I want two more bowls of noodles for takeaway.

48:16.610 --> 48:17.740
Okay, just a moment.

48:28.790 --> 48:29.530
Please hurry.

48:29.590 --> 48:30.340
I don't have much time.

48:30.390 --> 48:31.140
Okay, just a minute.

48:35.390 --> 48:36.460
Sir, how much is it?

48:36.790 --> 48:37.390
Twenty.

48:38.830 --> 48:39.590
Where is my money?

48:42.390 --> 48:43.240
Stop there!

48:43.510 --> 48:44.600
Did you take my money?

48:45.790 --> 48:46.730
Stop there!

48:47.110 --> 48:48.080
You grabbed my money!

48:48.180 --> 48:48.580
No...

48:48.580 --> 48:49.310
Show me.

48:49.350 --> 48:49.670
No.

48:49.670 --> 48:50.470
This is my money!

48:50.670 --> 48:51.070
Nope.

48:51.070 --> 48:51.760
Look, guys!

48:51.760 --> 48:52.710
She's a thief!

48:52.830 --> 48:53.930
She stole my money!

48:54.110 --> 48:54.590
No, I didn't.

48:54.630 --> 48:55.270
Give it to me!

48:55.470 --> 48:55.960
Look, guys!

48:55.960 --> 48:56.550
We've got the witness

48:56.750 --> 48:57.670
and physical evidence.

48:57.750 --> 48:58.540
That case can be closed.

48:58.750 --> 49:00.260
Call the police, guys!

49:00.620 --> 49:01.270
Take it out!

49:01.350 --> 49:02.280
Take it out now!

49:02.350 --> 49:03.790
I'll call the police if you don't take it out!

49:03.950 --> 49:04.710
What's going on?

49:04.870 --> 49:05.470
What are you doing?

49:05.490 --> 49:06.610
She stole my money!

49:07.000 --> 49:07.930
She's holding it!

49:09.070 --> 49:09.510
Take it out.

49:09.550 --> 49:10.190
S-She's caught you.

49:10.270 --> 49:10.990
Just give her the money.

49:11.020 --> 49:11.710
It's okay. We're the police.

49:11.790 --> 49:12.230
C'mon.

49:16.100 --> 49:16.550
Stop there!

49:16.670 --> 49:17.230
Stop!

49:18.570 --> 49:19.160
Stop there!

49:24.870 --> 49:25.480
What's going on?

49:25.580 --> 49:26.470
What happened?

49:26.630 --> 49:27.070
What's wrong?

49:27.150 --> 49:27.800
What...

49:28.430 --> 49:29.320
What's wrong?

49:29.790 --> 49:30.630
Call the ambulance. Hurry.

49:30.870 --> 49:31.430
Okay.

49:37.570 --> 49:38.630
She's lying on the floor.

49:40.470 --> 49:41.670
I don't think she's acting.

49:44.830 --> 49:45.390
We've

49:45.390 --> 49:46.430
thoroughly investigated it.

49:46.690 --> 49:47.870
It was a complete accident.

49:48.300 --> 49:49.670
Both of you did nothing wrong.

49:49.830 --> 49:50.510
So don't put

49:50.530 --> 49:51.680
too much pressure on yourselves.

49:52.150 --> 49:52.830
We've contacted

49:52.850 --> 49:54.040
her family.

49:54.190 --> 49:55.350
They have no objections.

49:55.750 --> 49:56.550
But her father

49:56.550 --> 49:57.430
has one request.

49:57.510 --> 49:58.570
That is

49:58.670 --> 49:59.510
to keep it on the down low.

49:59.830 --> 50:01.390
She's already gone, after all.

50:01.750 --> 50:02.920
Being suspected as a thief

50:02.950 --> 50:03.910
would add to the disgrace.

50:05.430 --> 50:06.590
No one expected you

50:06.670 --> 50:07.970
to run into this

50:08.350 --> 50:09.580
in your first mission.

50:10.100 --> 50:11.090
So you two

50:11.110 --> 50:12.790
should be mentally prepared.

50:13.310 --> 50:14.060
Got it.

50:14.710 --> 50:15.550
Thank you, Captain Jia.

50:16.150 --> 50:16.740
Captain Jia,

50:18.190 --> 50:18.910
I feel that I might

50:18.910 --> 50:20.310
not be suitable for frontline work.

50:31.550 --> 50:33.400
I request to leave the frontline temporarily.

50:33.650 --> 50:35.040
Hope you can approve.
